                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4786" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0147</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8153 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安钢大厦混合所有制改革的新模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The New Reform Model of Mixed Ownership of Angang Building</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">任广乾，徐瑞，李晓晓，刘忠东</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河南安钢大厦有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安钢大厦；混合所有制改革；合资；租赁；专业化运营</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Angang Building; Mixed Ownership Reform; Joint Venture; Lease; Specialized Operation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为省属大型国有企业安钢集团在省会的窗口，安钢大厦曾为服务安钢发展，树立安钢形象赢得不少赞誉。然而，随着市场经济的发展和郑州的崛起，酒店业竞争日趋激烈，因酒店设施老化，加上股权结构单一，体制机制不活，安钢大厦连年亏损，经营困难。面对严峻的市场形势，为脱危解困，集团公司成立安钢大厦改革工作组，坚持“因地施策、因业施策、因企施策，宜独则独、宜控则控、宜参则参”的原则，积极探索对外合作的模式，最后确定采取“合资＋租赁＋专业化经营”的混改新模式，解决了困扰多年的国有资产保全兼顾高效率专业化运营和人员安置等核心问题，产生了良好的政治效益、经济效益和社会效益。该案例为大型国有企业分离辅助业务和后勤服务板块提供了一个新的思路和方向，同时丰富了公司治理课程关于企业混合所有制改革新模式的素材。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a provincial large-scale state-owned enterprise Angang Group in the provincial capital window, Angang building has won the praise of the service of Angang Group. However, with the development of the market economy and the rise of Zhengzhou, the competition in the hotel and hotel industry has become increasingly fierce. Due to the aging of hotel equipment and facilities, and the single ownership structure, the institutional mechanism is not alive. In the face of severe market conditions, in order to get rid of the dangers, the group company set up the Angang building reform working group. “Insist on local policy, industry policy, and enterprise policy, it should be independent, control should be controlled, and it should be the principle of actively exploring the ways and modes of foreign cooperation, and finally adopting the mixed mode of “joint venture + leasing + specialized operation”, and solved the state-owned asset preservation and high-efficiency professional operation and personnel that have plagued the reform of state-owned enterprises for many years. Core issues such as resettlement have produced good political, economic and social benefits. This case provides a new idea and direction for the separation of auxiliary business and logistics services in large state-owned enterprises, and also enriches the material of corporate governance curriculum on the reform model of corporate mixed ownership.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理 混合所有制改革的原则、模式和效应。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
